1
00:00:00,220 --> 00:00:03,680
Marla's given us permission
to provide you with her CCD.

2
00:00:03,680 --> 00:00:07,846
Since she's fictional this is not
protected health information, so

3
00:00:07,846 --> 00:00:10,770
you can have it and freely use it.

4
00:00:10,770 --> 00:00:15,800
For this activity you should send
this CCD as an attachment, and

5
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:18,749
email it to your HealthVault
direct email address.

6
00:00:19,860 --> 00:00:23,430
Before doing that,
go to your message center settings, and

7
00:00:23,430 --> 00:00:28,880
make sure add incoming message
attachments as files is checked,

8
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:32,100
so the data in Marla's CCD
will be added to your record.

9
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:39,500
Once that's done, and you've imported
Marla's CCD into to your record.

10
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:43,420
Manually add the drug
Spiriva to Marla's record.

11
00:00:43,420 --> 00:00:47,010
This is a drug Dr. Jones might
prescribe to help her breathe better.

12
00:00:48,195 --> 00:00:53,945
Also manually add a new hemoglobin A1C,
with a level of 9.2%.

13
00:00:53,945 --> 00:00:56,905
You can date them both
the date you add them.

14
00:00:57,905 --> 00:00:59,805
Now go to health information and

15
00:00:59,805 --> 00:01:03,755
click more actions, and
export Marla's record as a CCD.

16
00:01:04,754 --> 00:01:07,415
You'll need to submit it to
get credit for this activity.
